[confidence=0.51 evi\n  - confidence: 0.62\n  - evidence: memory/2026-04-21.md:183-185\n  - recalls: 0\n  - status: staged\n- Candidate: User: Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists and follow it strictly. Use SOUL/IDENTITY/USER/MEMORY context when available for personalization. Do not continue unrelated old tasks or replay prior work. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK. When reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspac\n  - confidence: 0.58\n  - evidence: memory/.dreams/session-corpus/2026-04-21.txt:1-1\n  - recalls: 0\n  - status: staged\n- Candidate: Assistant: HEARTBEAT_OK\n  - confidence: 0.58\n  - evidence: memory/.dreams/session-corpus/2026-04-21.txt:2-2\n  - recalls: 0\n  - status: staged\n- Candidate: Assistant: 这次有 3 条很值得你关注，和你当前 OpenClaw 工作流直接贴合： 1. **Plan Mode 全量发布，几乎就是你“主控调度”思路的官方产品化** 它不再是单轮执行，而是“计划-执行-验证”的多步协作流。 对你来说，意义不只是多了个功能，而是 OpenClaw 官方产品路线，开始和你当前的“主控 + 多 Agent + 可追踪步骤”方法论对齐了。这个值得重点跟踪。 2. **Cron 自动重试，直接利好 heartbeat\n...[truncated]...\n```\nEND_QUOTED_NOTES\n\nA new session was started via /new or /reset. If runtime-provided startup context is included for this first turn, use it before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 23rd, 2026 - 9:40 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-23 13:40 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776951674647}}
