{"type":"message","id":"c45a373a","parentId":"9e235cd9","timestamp":"2026-04-23T14:00:58.715Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-04-23 21:56:40 GMT+8] Exec completed (marine-v, code 0) :: Using openai / gpt-image-1 for single Switch model: --model <id> | EXTEND.md default_model.openai | env OPENAI_IMAGE_MODEL /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-im…\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1776952855634-2e448451\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-23 22:00 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n愿意，但是你生成的UI界面的收藏按钮都变形了，还多出一个收藏🌟按钮出来，记得修复回来"}],"timestamp":1776952858667}}
{"type":"message","id":"36666b19","parentId":"c45a373a","timestamp":"2026-04-23T14:01:04.365Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_sKAfViAEb4k54E5ACVTqa2jH|fc_0fd125bcf7eca6390169ea261de33881939a4b5ecfeea752ee","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"offset":1,"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/using-superpowers/SKILL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"limit\":200,\"offset\":1,\"path\":\"~/.openclaw/skills/using-superpowers/SKILL.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":36572,"output":39,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36611,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776952858715,"responseId":"resp_0fd125bcf7eca6390169ea261bf42881938556d6a62fd0972f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"52ae822f","parentId":"36666b19","timestamp":"2026-04-23T14:01:04.464Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_sKAfViAEb4k54E5ACVTqa2jH|fc_0fd125bcf7eca6390169ea261de33881939a4b5ecfeea752ee","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: using-superpowers\ndescription: Use when starting any conversation - establishes how to find and use skills, requiring Skill tool invocation before ANY response including clarifying questions\n---\n\n<SUBAGENT-STOP>\nIf you were dispatched as a subagent to execute a specific task, skip this skill.\n</SUBAGENT-STOP>\n\n<EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>\nIf you think there is even a 1% chance a skill might apply to what you are doing, you ABSOLUTELY MUST invoke the skill.\n\nIF A SKILL APPLIES TO YOUR TASK, YOU DO NOT HAVE A CHOICE. YOU MUST USE IT.\n\nThis is not negotiable. This is not optional. You cannot rationalize your way out of this.\n</EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>\n\n## Instruction Priority\n\nSuperpowers skills override default system prompt behavior, but **user instructions always take precedence**:\n\n1. **User's explicit instructions** (CLAUDE.md, GEMINI.md, AGENTS.md, direct requests) — highest priority\n2. **Superpowers skills** — override default system behavior where they conflict\n3. **Default system prompt** — lowest priority\n\nIf CLAUDE.md, GEMINI.md, or AGENTS.md says \"don't use TDD\" and a skill says \"always use TDD,\" follow the user's instructions. The user is in control.\n\n## How to Access Skills\n\n**In Claude Code:** Use the `Skill` tool. When you invoke a skill, its content is loaded and presented to you—follow it directly. Never use the Read tool on skill files.\n\n**In Gemini CLI:** Skills activate via the `activate_skill` tool. Gemini loads skill metadata at session start and activates the full content on demand.\n\n**In other environments:** Check your platform's documentation for how skills are loaded.\n\n## Platform Adaptation\n\nSkills use Claude Code tool names. Non-CC platforms: see `references/codex-tools.md` (Codex) for tool equivalents. Gemini CLI users get the tool mapping loaded automatically via GEMINI.md.\n\n# Using Skills\n\n## The Rule\n\n**Invoke relevant or requested skills BEFORE any response or action.** Even a 1% chance a skill might apply means that you should invoke the skill to check. If an invoked skill turns out to be wrong for the situation, you don't need to use it.\n\n```dot\ndigraph skill_flow {\n    \"User message received\" [shape=doublecircle];\n    \"About to EnterPlanMode?\" [shape=doublecircle];\n    \"Already brainstormed?\" [shape=diamond];\n    \"Invoke brainstorming skill\" [shape=box];\n    \"Might any skill apply?\" [shape=diamond];\n    \"Invoke Skill tool\" [shape=box];\n    \"Announce: 'Using [skill] to [purpose]'\" [shape=box];\n    \"Has checklist?\" [shape=diamond];\n    \"Create TodoWrite todo per item\" [shape=box];\n    \"Follow skill exactly\" [shape=box];\n    \"Respond (including clarifications)\" [shape=doublecircle];\n\n    \"About to EnterPlanMode?\" -> \"Already brainstormed?\";\n    \"Already brainstormed?\" -> \"Invoke brainstorming skill\" [label=\"no\"];\n    \"Already brainstormed?\" -> \"Might any skill apply?\" [label=\"yes\"];\n    \"Invoke brainstorming skill\" -> \"Might any skill apply?\";\n\n    \"User message received\" -> \"Might any skill apply?\";\n    \"Might any skill apply?\" -> \"Invoke Skill tool\" [label=\"yes, even 1%\"];\n    \"Might any skill apply?\" -> \"Respond (including clarifications)\" [label=\"definitely not\"];\n    \"Invoke Skill tool\" -> \"Announce: 'Using [skill] to [purpose]'\";\n    \"Announce: 'Using [skill] to [purpose]'\" -> \"Has checklist?\";\n    \"Has checklist?\" -> \"Create TodoWrite todo per item\" [label=\"yes\"];\n    \"Has checklist?\" -> \"Follow skill exactly\" [label=\"no\"];\n    \"Create TodoWrite todo per item\" -> \"Follow skill exactly\";\n}\n```\n\n## Red Flags\n\nThese thoughts mean STOP—you're rationalizing:\n\n| Thought | Reality |\n|---------|---------|\n| \"This is just a simple question\" | Questions are tasks. Check for skills. |\n| \"I need more context first\" | Skill check comes BEFORE clarifying questions. |\n| \"Let me explore the codebase first\" | Skills tell you HOW to explore. Check first. |\n| \"I can check git/files quickly\" | Files lack conversation context. Check for skills. |\n| \"Let me gather information first\" | Skills tell you HOW to gather information. |\n| \"This doesn't need a formal skill\" | If a skill exists, use it. |\n| \"I remember this skill\" | Skills evolve. Read current version. |\n| \"This doesn't count as a task\" | Action = task. Check for skills. |\n| \"The skill is overkill\" | Simple things become complex. Use it. |\n| \"I'll just do this one thing first\" | Check BEFORE doing anything. |\n| \"This feels productive\" | Undisciplined action wastes time. Skills prevent this. |\n| \"I know what that means\" | Knowing the concept ≠ using the skill. Invoke it. |\n\n## Skill Priority\n\nWhen multiple skills could apply, use this order:\n\n1. **Process skills first** (brainstorming, debugging) - these determine HOW to approach the task\n2. **Implementation skills second** (frontend-design, mcp-builder) - these guide execution\n\n\"Let's build X\" → brainstorming first, then implementation skills.\n\"Fix this bug\" → debugging first, then domain-specific skills.\n\n## Skill Types\n\n**Rigid** (TDD, debugging): Follow exactly. Don't adapt away discipline.\n\n**Flexible** (patterns): Adapt principles to context.\n\nThe skill itself tells you which.\n\n## User Instructions\n\nInstructions say WHAT, not HOW. \"Add X\" or \"Fix Y\" doesn't mean skip workflows.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776952864425}}
{"type":"message","id":"35589316","parentId":"52ae822f","timestamp":"2026-04-23T14:01:37.504Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我来修这个，重点收紧 UI 结构，明确只保留一个正常的收藏按钮，避免多余星标和控件变形。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fd125bcf7eca6390169ea26234be48193942f1ba700ce849a\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4cMugj5Yphaf6GMjgviWJjHM|fc_0fd125bcf7eca6390169ea262590148193b9440fa4476a0d6f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"if command -v bun >/dev/null 2>&1; then BUN_X=bun; else BUN_X='npx -y bun'; fi; $BUN_X ~/.openclaw/skills/baoyu-imagine/scripts/main.ts --provider openai --model gpt-image-1 --prompt \"生成一张进一步精修的真实手机竖屏中文短视频平台直播截图，继续沿用上一版‘更像原生直播 UI’方向，但这次重点修复 UI 控件错误。主体是一位神似美国知名电动车公司创始人的中年白人男性，短发，自然兴奋地在直播间推销一罐中国凉茶。直播桌前有整齐摆放的凉茶、麦克风、补光灯、手机支架、产品架、价格牌，背景是饱满真实的中文带货直播间。\n\n关键修复要求：\n1. 右侧互动按钮区只保留一套自然、统一、未变形的直播平台常见按钮，图标比例正常，边缘清晰，不要拉伸。\n2. 收藏按钮只能出现一次，而且必须是正常、清晰、未变形的单个收藏按钮，不要额外再出现一个星形收藏按钮，不要重复收藏入口，不要多余的星标 UI。\n3. 所有 UI 元素排布要符合真实直播 app 逻辑，不能重叠、错位、漂浮。\n4. 底部评论区、弹幕、在线人数、点赞数、礼物提示、商品卡片都保留，但层级清晰，不要挤压到右侧按钮区。\n5. 中文文字尽量简短清楚可读，不要乱码，不要错别字，不要出现奇怪重复控件。\n6. 整体必须像真实用户保存的直播截屏，不是海报，不是设计稿。\n\n画面要求：真实感强，高细节，轻微手机压缩感和少量噪点，构图自然，略带荒诞幽默但优先真实。不要插画风，不要卡通风，不要人物畸形，不要多余手指，不要水印，不要过度磨皮，不要背景空。\" --image /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/douyin-live-herbal-tea-screenshot-v2-ui-fixed.png --ar 9:16 --quality 2k","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":900},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"if command -v bun >/dev/null 2>&1; then BUN_X=bun; else BUN_X='npx -y bun'; fi; $BUN_X ~/.openclaw/skills/baoyu-imagine/scripts/main.ts --provider openai --model gpt-image-1 --prompt \\\"生成一张进一步精修的真实手机竖屏中文短视频平台直播截图，继续沿用上一版‘更像原生直播 UI’方向，但这次重点修复 UI 控件错误。主体是一位神似美国知名电动车公司创始人的中年白人男性，短发，自然兴奋地在直播间推销一罐中国凉茶。直播桌前有整齐摆放的凉茶、麦克风、补光灯、手机支架、产品架、价格牌，背景是饱满真实的中文带货直播间。\\n\\n关键修复要求：\\n1. 右侧互动按钮区只保留一套自然、统一、未变形的直播平台常见按钮，图标比例正常，边缘清晰，不要拉伸。\\n2. 收藏按钮只能出现一次，而且必须是正常、清晰、未变形的单个收藏按钮，不要额外再出现一个星形收藏按钮，不要重复收藏入口，不要多余的星标 UI。\\n3. 所有 UI 元素排布要符合真实直播 app 逻辑，不能重叠、错位、漂浮。\\n4. 底部评论区、弹幕、在线人数、点赞数、礼物提示、商品卡片都保留，但层级清晰，不要挤压到右侧按钮区。\\n5. 中文文字尽量简短清楚可读，不要乱码，不要错别字，不要出现奇怪重复控件。\\n6. 整体必须像真实用户保存的直播截屏，不是海报，不是设计稿。\\n\\n画面要求：真实感强，高细节，轻微手机压缩感和少量噪点，构图自然，略带荒诞幽默但优先真实。不要插画风，不要卡通风，不要人物畸形，不要多余手指，不要水印，不要过度磨皮，不要背景空。\\\" --image /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/douyin-live-herbal-tea-screenshot-v2-ui-fixed.png --ar 9:16 --quality 2k\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":1000,\"timeout\":900}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":37868,"output":625,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38493,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776952864466,"responseId":"resp_0fd125bcf7eca6390169ea2621dcc48193b731179308ce5dc2"}}
